# Roo Code Integration

## Overview

Roo Code integration adds diff-based editing capabilities to EscapeKit MCP.

## Features

- Apply unified diffs programmatically
- Generate diffs between code versions
- Validate diff format
- Fuzzy matching for robust application

## CLI Usage

```bash
qwen-escapekit diff apply <file> <diff> [--fuzzy <n>] [--backup]
qwen-escapekit diff generate <original> <modified> [